title: This Week In Space podcast: Episode 188 — A New NASA Leader Rises?
description: On Episode 188 of This Week In Space, Rod Pyle and Tariq Malik discuss Jared Isaacman, the billionaire entrepreneur and private astronaut, who took had his second confirmation as NASA's next leader.
